bookTitle: Anastasia: The Last Grand Duchess, Russia, 1914
Plot: Award-winning author Carolyn Meyer introduces readers to the unforgettable Anastasia Romanov whose idyllic life is forever changed with the coming of World War I.
Characters: Grand Duchess Anastasia Nikolaevna of Russia
Setting: Tsarskoye Selo (Russian Federation), Tobolsk (Russian Federation), Livadiya (Ukraine)
